description: With this skill, you can find locations and times for karaoke in the Tricities Washington. This skill will give you all available locations and times, plus give addresses as a card in your Alexa App.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Tricities Karaoke where can I sing tonight
Alexa, ask Tricities Karaoke who has Karaoke tonight
Alexa, ask Tricities Karaoke what places have karaoke tonight
name: Tricities Karaoke
shortDescription: Find local karaoke in the Tricities Washington.
